'''Luka Yovetich''' (stage name '''Luka Jones''')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dornsife.usc.edu/news/stories/1125/breakout-act/ |title=Breakout Act > News > USC Dornsife |publisher=Dornsife.usc.edu |date= |accessdate=2012-07-09}}</ref> is an [[Americans|American]] actor and comedian, best known for co-starring in the [[National Broadcasting Company|NBC]] sitcoms ''[[Best Friends Forever (TV series)|Best Friends Forever]]'' and ''[[Up All Night (TV series)|Up All Night]]''.
